  <abstract>Highlander brochure advertising their workshops on segregation in summer of 1954. Workshop topics include history of segregation, recent progress, state attitudes toward the Supreme Court decision, and planning follow-up programs. The pamphlet outlines a daily schedule and includes a basic overview of Highlander and future activities. This particular brochure was sent to Merl Eppse.</abstract>
